data.description: Looking for space in Effingham? This home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, office, and a sunroom. There is an above ground pool with a screened enclosure. There is a view of the pond on the backside of the home. This property has 51 acres (4 lots) horse stables, workshop, RV connection, and a generator. NO HOA for this property, and there is a mobile home on the back of the property that was used for a hunting stand
